1:05:56.244 --> 1:06:01.499
Sometimes I... I wish

1:05:56.244 --> 1:06:01.499
I was more like that.

1:06:01.625 --> 1:06:04.544
Anyway, I'm sorry.

1:06:05.378 --> 1:06:06.963
It's OK.

1:06:08.673 --> 1:06:12.928
I'm kind of realizing

1:06:08.673 --> 1:06:12.928
that work isn't everything.

1:06:13.052 --> 1:06:16.097
I guess being back

1:06:13.052 --> 1:06:16.097
on the island gave me

1:06:16.222 --> 1:06:18.892
a different perspective

1:06:16.222 --> 1:06:18.892
on things.

1:06:20.226 --> 1:06:23.146
I kind of feel like

1:06:20.226 --> 1:06:23.146
I'm home again.

1:06:23.271 --> 1:06:27.233
Something about this place,

1:06:23.271 --> 1:06:27.233
I guess, just...

1:06:27.358 --> 1:06:31.237
This island just

1:06:27.358 --> 1:06:31.237
helps people see clearly.

1:06:33.949 --> 1:06:39.329
-Must be that island magic.

1:06:33.949 --> 1:06:39.329
-Must be.

1:06:39.454 --> 1:06:42.958
