1:06:39.454 --> 1:06:42.958
Home isn't a place.

1:06:39.454 --> 1:06:42.958
It's a feeling.

1:06:43.082 --> 1:06:46.085
And, you know,

1:06:43.082 --> 1:06:46.085
I'm starting to realize

1:06:46.210 --> 1:06:50.173
what you've been saying about

1:06:46.210 --> 1:06:50.173
not wanting to leave this place.

1:06:53.050 --> 1:06:55.470
So I've had an idea.

1:06:55.595 --> 1:06:58.097
Oh, more reading. Great!

1:06:58.222 --> 1:07:01.685
