1:07:01.810 --> 1:07:04.729
If you accept the role as CEO,

1:07:04.855 --> 1:07:08.107
company headquarters will

1:07:04.855 --> 1:07:08.107
be moved to the island.

1:07:08.232 --> 1:07:10.527
That way, you don't

1:07:08.232 --> 1:07:10.527
have to move away

1:07:10.652 --> 1:07:14.405
-and you can keep your charity.

1:07:10.652 --> 1:07:14.405
-Laura...

1:07:14.531 --> 1:07:18.869
It could take a year or two,

1:07:14.531 --> 1:07:18.869
