1:07:14.531 --> 1:07:18.869
would work.

1:07:20.453 --> 1:07:22.914
What do you think?

1:07:24.875 --> 1:07:26.960
I think I'm running

1:07:24.875 --> 1:07:26.960
out of excuses.

1:07:27.084 --> 1:07:31.464
I'm surrounded

1:07:27.084 --> 1:07:31.464
