1:07:42.600 --> 1:07:44.602
Do you know how rare that is?

1:07:46.938 --> 1:07:48.314
It sounds like someone I know.

1:07:51.985 --> 1:07:53.695
Did you work

1:07:51.985 --> 1:07:53.695
on this all night?

1:07:53.820 --> 1:07:58.324
Yeah. Well, I am

1:07:53.820 --> 1:07:58.324
a bit of a nerd so...

1:08:00.952 --> 1:08:03.079
No.

1:08:03.204 --> 1:08:04.998
You're incredible.

1:08:13.048 --> 1:08:14.424
[footsteps approach]

1:08:17.969 --> 1:08:20.680
-[man] That was worth the hike!

1:08:17.969 --> 1:08:20.680
-[woman] Yeah, it was.

1:08:25.101 --> 1:08:28.688
-[man] Coming through.

1:08:25.101 --> 1:08:28.688
-[Gem] Let's go. Let's go.

1:08:25.101 --> 1:08:28.688
Lots to do, people.

